{ ============================================================================
  libcosy — modular ROSY port of COSY INFINITY 10.2 (cosy.fox)

  Entrypoint. Bring all of libcosy into scope with:

      INCLUDE 'libcosy';       { resolves to libcosy/mod.rosy }

  This relies on the directory-fallback behavior added to INCLUDE in v0.36.0.
  ============================================================================ }

BEGIN;

INCLUDE 'globals.rosy';      { shared global state (MAP, RAY, fields, flags, ...) }
INCLUDE 'helpers';           { non-physics: math, strings, polynomial, IO, ...   }
INCLUDE 'physics';           { reference particle, maps, elements, tracking, ... }

END;
